#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.77"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.77:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.77:0.2"
msgid "8. Apaṇṇakavagga "
msgstr "8. Guaranteed "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.77:0.3"
msgid "77. Acinteyyasutta "
msgstr "77. Unthinkable "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.77:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, acinteyyāni, na cintetabbāni; yāni cintento ummādassa vighātassa bhāgī assa. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these four things are unthinkable. They should not be thought about, and anyone who tries to think about them will go mad or get frustrated. "

msgctxt "an4.77:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.77:1.3"
msgid "Buddhānaṃ, bhikkhave, buddhavisayo acinteyyo, na cintetabbo; "
msgstr "The scope of the Buddhas … "

msgctxt "an4.77:1.4"
msgid "yaṃ cintento ummādassa vighātassa bhāgī assa. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.77:1.5"
msgid "Jhāyissa, bhikkhave, jhānavisayo acinteyyo, na cintetabbo; "
msgstr "The scope of one in absorption … "

msgctxt "an4.77:1.6"
msgid "yaṃ cintento ummādassa vighātassa bhāgī assa. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.77:1.7"
msgid "Kammavipāko, bhikkhave, acinteyyo, na cintetabbo; "
msgstr "The results of deeds … "

msgctxt "an4.77:1.8"
msgid "yaṃ cintento ummādassa vighātassa bhāgī assa. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.77:1.9"
msgid "Lokacintā, bhikkhave, acinteyyā, na cintetabbā; "
msgstr "Speculation about the world … "

msgctxt "an4.77:1.10"
msgid "yaṃ cintento ummādassa vighātassa bhāgī assa. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.77:1.11"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri acinteyyāni, na cintetabbāni; yāni cintento ummādassa vighātassa bhāgī assā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the four unthinkable things. They should not be thought about, and anyone who tries to think about them will go mad or get frustrated.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.77:1.12"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
